### ========================================
### PRUEBAS DE SIMULACIÓN WEBPAY - 4 ESCENARIOS
### ========================================

### 1. OBTENER ESCENARIOS DISPONIBLES
GET http://localhost:8081/api/webpay-simulation/simulate/scenarios
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. OBTENER ESCENARIO ACTUAL
GET http://localhost:8081/api/webpay-simulation/simulate/scenario
Content-Type: application/json

### ========================================
### ESCENARIO 1: PAGO EXITOSO
### ========================================

### Configurar escenario de pago exitoso
POST http://localhost:8081/api/webpay-simulation/simulate/scenario
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "scenario": "SUCCESS"
}

### Iniciar pago exitoso
POST http://localhost:8081/api/webpay-simulation/simulate/init
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "pedidoId": 1001,
    "monto": 25000
}

