### ========================================
### CONSULTAS DE ESTADO
### ========================================

### Consultar estado de transacción (reemplazar TOKEN_AQUI con el token real)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/webpay-simulation/simulate/status/TOKEN_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

### Obtener todas las transacciones
GET http://localhost:8081/api/webpay-simulation/simulate/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

### ========================================
### ADMINISTRACIÓN
### ========================================

### Limpiar todas las transacciones
DELETE http://localhost:8081/api/webpay-simulation/simulate/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

### ========================================
### ACCESO A PANELES WEB
### ========================================

### Panel de Control de Simulación
GET http://localhost:8081/api/webpay-simulation/simulate/panel

